    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. Test conditions factor achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3; this shortfall is accepted because the ASTM F1717 standard prescribes a single load configuration and the QoI comparison metrics are well within acceptance bounds for all three quantities of interest. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for the non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending COU.",
